# Force LF on checkout on every platform (crlfcheckout, C.1.3.2). The framework is
# bundled into each adapter's dist; LF-stable sources keep the bundle byte-exact.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.zip binary
